quran[3{c,v,t}:
5,3,"tum par haraam kya gaya Murdaar, khoon, soor ka gosht, woh janwar jo khuda ke siwa kisi aur ke naam par zibah kya gaya ho, woh jo ghulla ghatt kar, ya chout kha kar, ya bulandi se gir kar, ya takkar kha kar mra ho, ya jisay kisi darendey ne pharha ho siwaye is ke jisay tum ne zindah paker zibah kar liya aur woh jo kisi Aasta ne par zibah kya gaya ho neez yeh bhi tumahray liye najaaiz hai ke panson ke zareya se apni qismat maloom karo yeh sab af-aal fisq hain aaj kafiroon ko tumahray deen ki taraf se poori mayoosi ho chuki hai lehaza tum unn se nah daro balkay mujh se daro aaj mein ne tumahray deen ko tumahray liye mukammal kar diya hai aur apni Nemat tum par tamam kar di hai aur tumahray liye islam ko tumahray deen ki hesiyat se qubool kar liya hai ( lehaza haraam o halal ki jo quyood tum par aed kar di gayi hain unn ki paband y karo ) Albata jo shakhs bhook se majaboor ho kar unn mein se koi cheez kha le, baghair is ke ke gunah ki taraf is ka melaan ho to bay shak Allah maaf karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
5,4,"log puchhte hain ke un ke liye kya halal kya gaya hai, kaho tumahray liye saari pak cheeze halal kar di gayi hain aur jin shikari janwaron ko tum ne sadhaeya ho jin ko khuda ke diye hue ilm ki bana par tum shikaar ki taleem diya karte ho woh jis janwar ko tumahray liye pakar rakhen is ko bhi tum kha saktayho, Albata is par Allah ka naam le lau aur Allah ka qanoon tornay se daro, Allah ko hisaab letay kuch der nahi lagti"
5,5,"aaj tumahray liye saari pak cheeze halal kar di gayi hain ahal kitaab ka khana tumahray liye halal hai aur tumhara khana unn ke liye aur mehfooz aurtain bhi tumahray liye halal hain khuwa woh ahal imaan ke giroh se hon ya unn qomon mein se jin ko tum se pehlay kitaab di gayi thi, bashar tik_h tum unn ke mohar ada kar ke nikah mein unn ke Muhafiz bano, nah yeh ke azad shehwat rani karne lagu ya chori chupay آ(ashnaiya-nkaro aur jo kisi ne imaan ki rawish par chalne se inkaar kya to is ka sara karnaama zindagi zaya ho jaye ga aur woh akhirat mein dewalia hoga"
